":2018764,"uid":55177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"acfe0538c4f2cdfa657914919f970080f23cc172","tid":2018764,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b5f549863de29001332ef9ced6f547d2f8b4306","tid":2018764,"uid":102850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:59:14.000Z","msg":"唔辣點香"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T22:00:42.000Z","msg":"香而不辣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T22:56:56.000Z","msg":"大把印度咖哩唔辣， 牛油雞， rogan josh,  masala <br />\n<br />\n至於邊到食就唔知<br />\n可能正宗印度阿叔有得食？ <br />\n<br />\n未係香港食過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835f9595007a8a0e09ddb9564dafb259272cb89b","tid":2018764,"uid":78167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T23:00:03.000Z","msg":"咖哩唔一定要辣先香, 香唔香主要睇煮法同香料既配搭(丁香, 八角, 咖哩葉, 香茅, 黃薑等等),   <br />\n<br />\n偏向唔辣/少辣既話泰式有黃咖哩, 馬沙立咖哩, Panang咖哩 。<br />\n我自己間唔中會整娘惹咖哩 (偏香濃, 睇人煮法可能會少辣但通常唔會好似泰式青/紅咁辣)。<br />\n另外印度既代表有 korma, pasanda 呢啲完全唔辣既咖哩。<br />\n<br />\n香港既餐廳就無乜特別推介, 我通常出 trip東南亞國家 / 印度都會周圍試啲唔同咖哩, 自己間唔中有舖癮都會買野自己煮"},{"pid":"97bb18bfc774fede9ed332ef7f5d037ec6736254","tid":2018764,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b5f549863de29001332ef9ced6f547d2f8b4306","tid":2018764,"uid":102850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:59:14.000Z","msg":"唔辣點香"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T00:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}